  "content": [
    {
      "type": "source_page",
      "blockVersion": 1,
      "title": {
        "ar": "معالجة التنزيل",
        "en": "The hardship of revelation"
      },
      "text": {
        "ar": "تسجل هذه الصفحة وصف ابن عباس لشدة معالجة النبي ﷺ للتنزيل ومبادارته لتحريك شفتيه حفظاً، وما نزل في ذلك من النهي الإلهي والتطمين في سورة القيامة.",
        "en": "This page records Ibn 'Abbas's description of the Prophet's ﷺ hardship in bearing revelation and his rushing to move his lips to memorize it, and the divine prohibition and reassurance that came down regarding this in Surat al-Qiyamah."
      },
      "sourceRef": {
        "ar": "كتاب بدء الوحي، ص ١٥٧",
        "en": "Book of Revelation, p. 157"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "page_annotations",
      "blockVersion": 1,
      "entries": [
        {
          "id": "page-5-source-quran-preservation",
          "kind": "scholarly_annotation",
          "title": {
            "ar": "ضمان حفظ القرآن",
            "en": "Guarantee of the Quran's preservation"
          },
          "scholar": {
            "ar": "النووي",
            "en": "al-Nawawi"
          },
          "work": {
            "ar": "شرح مسلم",
            "en": "Sharh Muslim"
          },
          "note": {
            "ar": "يبرز هذا الحديث تكفل الله بجمع القرآن في صدر النبي ﷺ وحفظه من النسيان، وهو من أعظم أدلة العصمة في التبليغ.",
            "en": "This hadith highlights God's guarantee to gather the Quran in the Prophet's ﷺ chest and protect it from being forgotten, which is among the greatest proofs of infallibility in transmission."
          },
          "citation": {
            "title": {
              "ar": "شرح مسلم",
